  cardName: "Binh L\u01B0\u01A1ng Th\u1ED1n \u0110o\u1EA1n"
  cardImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a82882394dd88604e998a2fefdc5dd01, type: 3}
  cardDescription: "Giai \u0111o\u1EA1n h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng, b\u1EA1n s\u1EED
    d\u1EE5ng l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y l\xEAn 1 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i kh\xE1c c\xF3
    kho\u1EA3ng c\xE1ch l\xE0 1 v\xE0 kh\xF4ng c\xF3 [Binh L\u01B0\u01A1ng Th\u1ED1n
    \u0110o\u1EA1n] trong khu v\u1EF1c ph\xE1n x\xE9t c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD.\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1EA1n
    ph\xE1n x\xE9t c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i, n\u1EBFu h\u1ECD
    c\xF3 [Binh L\u01B0\u01A1ng Th\u1ED1n \u0110o\u1EA1n] trong khu v\u1EF1c ph\xE1n
    x\xE9t, h\u1ECD ti\u1EBFn h\xE0nh 1 l\u1EA7n ph\xE1n x\xE9t, n\u1EBFu k\u1EBFt
    qu\u1EA3 ph\xE1n x\xE9t tr\xEAn l\xE0:\r\nCh\u1EA5t \u2663: h\u1ECD b\u1ECF \u0111i
    l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y.\r\nKh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i ch\u1EA5t \u2663: h\u1ECD b\u1ECF
    qua giai \u0111o\u1EA1n r\xFAt b\xE0i trong l\u01B0\u1EE3t n\xE0y v\xE0 b\u1ECF
    \u0111i l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y. b\xE0i."
